Instance Method# getType

DriverKit 19.0+macOS

```
IOHIDElementType getType();
```

## [Return Value](/documentation/hiddriverkit/iohidelement/gettype#return-value)

Returns the element type. Types are defined by the IOHIDElementType enumerator in [`IOHIDElementType`](/documentation/hiddriverkit/iohidelementtype).
